{"tid":2427050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"眾新聞 【初選大搜捕】 關尚義：香港似一個大扣留所","createTime":"2021-02-28T13:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T13:59:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"668a3b7d7be428f00f14da9ba81bec0ced2eebe1","tid":2427050,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"眾新聞<br />\n【初選大搜捕】<br />\n關尚義：香港似一個大扣留所<br />\nFeb 28, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e9RV1mNnTvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe9RV1mNnTvs&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=32e42a36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e9RV1mNnTvs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n60.5K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n民主派初選案中47人被控串謀顛覆國家政權，8人獲准保釋。美籍律師關尚義是其中一名獲准保釋的民主派人士，5月4日再報到。他見記者時提醒：「大家知道5月4號中國歷史上好緊要日子，係講自由民主、學生運動⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n他又引述律師朋友說香港自由逐漸減少，不論是教育或新聞自由，權利越來越收窄，「越來越似一個大嘅扣留所」。"},{"pid":"1a42344da64d377b5b2b89da99fad69687747c90","tid":2427050,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:50:15.000Z","msg":"真東柏林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2774538f76088394be628c87ea15a099eb1c49d","tid":2427050,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"呀叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}